headline: BlackRock® Canada Announces Final November Cash Distributions for the iShares® Premium Money Market ETF
summary: TORONTO, Nov. 20, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- BlackRock Asset Management Canada Limited (“BlackRock Canada”), an indirect, wholly-owned subsidiary of BlackRock, Inc. (NYSE: BLK), today announced the final November 2024 cash distributions for the iShares Premium Money Market ETF. Unitholders of record on November 21, 2024 will receive cash distributions payable on December 2, 2024. headline: BlackRock's Bitcoin ETF Options Soar to $1.9B on Debut, Fueling Bitcoin's Surge to New All-Time Highs
summary: BlackRock’s iShares Bitcoin Trust (IBIT) ETF options, launched on Nov. 19, 2024, saw an unprecedented $1.9 billion in notional exposure on its first day of trading.
